text: The Ministry of Nature Management and Ecology of the Republic of Bashkortostan(, ) is an agency of the government of Bashkortostan, headquartered in 28, Lenin Street, Ufa. == Ministers == After the 2019 Head of the Ministry has been Ural Iskandarov. ==References== ==External links== *Ministry of Nature Management and Ecology (Bashkortostan) Category:Politics of Bashkortostan
